[metadata]
Name:Coral Atoll unless-return
Goal:Win
Turns:4
Difficulty:Easy
Description:Verify Coral Atoll's ETB trigger: "sacrifice it unless you return an untapped Island you control to its owner's hand." P0 plays Coral Atoll while controlling an untapped Island. The trigger should fire; P0 pays the UnlessCost by returning the Island (ReturnToHand unless-cost path). Regression for mtg-939 (Return<N/Type> UnlessCost path).

